      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get the coin thing. but it still feels kind of like magic or something. like if there's no physical connection between them, how is the information actually getting across? is there some kind of underlying \"mechanism\" that makes it work, or is it just a weird rule of the universe we have to accept?",
      "source": "evaluator"
